NAME
    MooseX::DeclareX::Plugin::singleton - shiny syntax for MooseX::Singleton

SYNOPSIS
     class Logger is singleton
     {
        method log ($str) {
           ...;
        }
     }
 
     Logger->instance->log("here we are!");

DESCRIPTION
    This distribution extends MooseX::DeclareX with a new plugin:

    `is singleton`
        Marks a class as a singleton, providing `instance` and `initialize`
        methods as per MooseX::Singleton.

BUGS
    Known issue: you may occasionally get errors about inlining the
    constructor.

    Please report any bugs to
    <http://rt.cpan.org/Dist/Display.html?Queue=MooseX-DeclareX-Plugin-singlet
    on>.

SEE ALSO
    MooseX::DeclareX, MooseX::Singleton.

